dc_description_s: This point shapefile represents points of interest in Oaxaca (Mexico) that can include locations of police and fire stations, hospitals, educational institutions, libraries, historical sites, sports facilities, churches, and shopping. LeadDog Consulting (Originator and Publisher) has a Mexico-based data partner network for which they have access to GIS data sets to create city streets maps for Mexico, which may include streets, street names, street classifications, points of interests, landuse, water, neighborhood points, and railroads. These data are intended for geographic display and analysis at the city level. No responsibility is assumed by LeadDog Consulting. Instituto Nacional de Estadística, Geografía e Informática (Mexico) and LeadDog Consulting. (2010). Points of Interest: Oaxaca, Mexico, 2010. LeadDog Consulting. Available at: http://purl.stanford.edu/qv845zn1647. This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
